SELECT [Time Dimension tbl].[Week Ending Sunday], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Total Weighted]) AS [SumOfTotal Weighted], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Total Unweighted]) AS [SumOfTotal Unweighted], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Allegra Weighted]) AS [SumOfAllegra Weighted], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Allegra Percentage]) AS [SumOfAllegra Percentage], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Benedryl Weighted]) AS [SumOfBenedryl Weighted], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Benedryl Percentage]) AS [SumOfBenedryl Percentage], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Claritin Weighted]) AS [SumOfClaritin Weighted], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Claritin Percentage]) AS [SumOfClaritin Percentage], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Zyrtec Weighted]) AS [SumOfZyrtec Weighted], Sum([Keller Fay tbl].[Zyrtec Percentage]) AS [SumOfZyrtec Percentage] FROM [Time Dimension tbl] LEFT JOIN [Keller Fay tbl] ON [Time Dimension tbl].Date = [Keller Fay tbl].Date GROUP BY [Time Dimension tbl].[Week Ending Sunday];
